               <msContents>
                  <summary/>
                  
                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                        <title type="complete" ref="LIT4599Salot"/> 
                        <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                        <incipit xml:lang="gez">ጸሎት፡ በእንተ፡ ማዕሠሮሙ፡ ለአጋንንት፡ ወባርያ፡ ወሌጌዎን፡ ቡዳ፡</incipit>
                     </msItem>
                  
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2">
                     <title type="complete" ref="LIT4600Salot"/> 
                     <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">ጸሎት፡ ዘድንጋፄ፡ ዘወሀቦ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ለአዳም፡</incipit>
                     <note>The prayer is followed by other magical words.</note>
                  </msItem>
                  
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i3">
                     <title type="complete" ref="LIT4601Salot"/> 
                     <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">ጸሎት፡ በእንተ፡ ሕማመ፡ ቡዳ፡ ወነሀቢ፡ ጸፍልል፡ ደንፍል፡</incipit>
                  </msItem>
                  
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i4">
                     <title type="complete" ref="LIT4602MagicPr"/> 
                     <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">በስመ፡ አብ፡ <gap reason="omitted" extent="unknown" resp="PRS9622Ullendor"/>
                     በቅድስት፡ ሥላሴ፡ እንዘ፡ አአምን፡ ወእትመሐፀን፡ እክህደከ፡ ሳይጣን፡ ወቡዳ፡ እኩይ፡  አርዌ፡ ቀዳማዊ፡ ፀረ፡ አቡነ፡ አዳም፡</incipit>
                     <note>Ends with a prayer for the banning of all sorts of evils and diseases, such as
                        <foreign xml:lang="gez">ጋኔነ፡ ቀትር፡</foreign> (cf. Psalm 91:6, the Septuagint's
                        <foreign xml:lang="grc">δαιμονίου μεσημβρινοῦ</foreign> for the Hebrew 
                        <foreign xml:lang="he">יָשׁ֥וּד צָהֳרָֽיִם</foreign>), <foreign xml:lang="gez">ሕማመ፡ ዓይነት፡ ወእስ፡</foreign>, etc.</note>
                  </msItem>
                  
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i5">
                     <title type="complete" ref="LIT4603Salot"/> 
                     <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">ጸሎት፡ በእንተ፡ ሕማመ፡ ልብ፡</incipit>
                     <note>The prayer contains magical names and consists of five lines only.</note>
                  </msItem>
                  
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i6">
                     <title type="complete" ref="LIT4604Salot"/> 
                     <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">ጸሎት፡ በእንተ፡ ሕማመ፡ ቍርጸት፡</incipit>
                     <note>Magical formulae</note>
                  </msItem>
                  
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i7">
                     <title type="complete" ref="LIT4605Salot"/> 
                     <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">ጸሎት፡ በእንተ፡ ሕማመ፡ ስቅስቃት፡</incipit>
                  </msItem>
